entries.title: el nino diablo
entries.description: el nino diablo’s sound is conceptual and experimental -   fusing organic sounds, field recordings, live instrumentation with synths and drum machines. entries.title: Mountain Man Steve
entries.description: The moniker comes from my kids who coined the term after I returned from a backpacking trip sporting a full, bright red beard. Since I love the outdoors and actually grew up living on a mountain (at 3,849ft Mt. Diablo just barely qualifies), the nickname sorta stuck.
